            "title": "盤中速報 - 防特網(FTNT-US)大跌5.03%，報76.6美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>防特網(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:FTNT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/FTNT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">FTNT-US</a>)截至台北時間10日22:19股價下跌4.06美元，報76.60美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量2,202,675（股），盤中最高價80.52美元、最低價76.59美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.23%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.19%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.57%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.2%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>防特網(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:FTNT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/FTNT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">FTNT-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-2.27%</li> <li>近 1 月：-3.76%</li> <li>近 3 月：+1.82%</li> <li>近 6 月：-6.42%</li> <li>今年以來：+1.57%</li></ul></section></main>",
